            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/893.-step-1new-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip your <strong>rosemary leaves</strong> from their stems, discard the stems</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic cloves</strong> by pressing them down with the side of a knife (skins on!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1612438552834-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1612438552834-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1612438552834-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1612438552834-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1612438552834-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>breasts portion[s]</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong>, <strong>crushed garlic</strong> and<strong> rosemary leaves</strong></p><p>Season everything with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>,<strong> </strong>drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1599128733920-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1599128733920-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
