    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has been cooking for 20 min, trim, then add your <strong>green beans </strong>to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min or until tender</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return them to the pot and cover until serving</p>",
