    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the beans are cooking, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>sun-dried tomatoes</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced spring onion, chopped sun-dried tomatoes</strong> and<strong> tomato paste</strong> with 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook for 1 min</p>",
