    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> finely on a clean board</p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced chicken</strong> over the <strong>sun-dried tomato sauce</strong> with the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong>, <strong>roasted garlic</strong> (watch out for the skins!) and <strong>green beans</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
